{
  "stem": "1415.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Whenever everybody used to get together, and when it was, like, off time and we felt a little secure, and there were not too many Germans and they were only at the posts, and we were-- so we felt a little more free.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So they used to say, sing, and I used to sing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And even though I was let into the camp, and at times I felt free.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But when the Germans used to come into our camp, I remember my brothers always tell me to hide.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So I used to crawl under those-- those bunks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "There was a crawl space, and I used to crawl under and hide.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Because as a child, you were never secure anywhere.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Doesn't matter whether you worked or you didn't work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It depended on their moods, how they felt, and what transpired.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The whole war didn't make very much sense.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Nothing really made sense.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Living through it, I cannot make sense of anything that I went through.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was never conspicuous.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I learned that right away-- learned in order to survive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is not the time to show off.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was no showing off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this is how I found out that the people in the camp didn't-- didn't feel comfortable with me around either.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because when I used to disappear myself, so to speak, they were in jeopardy, because I used to hide amongst crowds.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Wherever there was a crowd or we had to stand up and be counted somewhere, I used to be in the back or between and never up front.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And not in the back either, because if they went around us I would be in the back.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I had to try to be in the middle somewhere.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they didn't like it.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
